{"tid":1471071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣招募］青衣文宣，機場過後立刻加強宣傳！！","createTime":"2019-08-14T07:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:54:03.000Z","uid":199622,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62691bc32f654ca85e389a5472e0b96a04b64655","tid":1471071,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:40:33.000Z","msg":"我們是青衣文宣，主要專注於青衣的宣傳工作，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=7faca31e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n經過琴日一戰，功效眾說紛紜，但有樣野係必須要做更多。<br />\n<br />\n就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋嚟緊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">16、17號會係青衣城派傳單</span></span>，內容有關嚟緊18號大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道人數唔多會相當危險。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋喺到舉行<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">招募</span></span> ，請青衣島人、街坊來幫手。<br />\n<br />\n18號係<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">非常重要</span></span>，關乎於係運動<span style=\"color: red;\">生死存亡</span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔想輸嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻入嚟幫手！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=7faca31e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們是一群為了令運動繼續保留溫度而聚在一起的人，從而令政府不能逃避問責的責任。<br />\n<br />\n運動發展至今，政府仍未回應訴求，很多香港人都感到無力， 甚至憤怒。但我們已沒有退讓的餘地，沒有放棄的成本，只能有一起對準目標，因為政府有無數施政欺壓平民。<br />\n<br />\n如果你懷著相同理念，想出多一分力，行多一小步。 我們現在誠意邀請你加入我們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果要keep住做更多既事，如banner或者放映會，就真係好需要人力幫手，因此我哋喺度想招募三種人才：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">活躍的天才</span></span><br />\n有心發表建設性意見。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">超級設計師</span></span><br />\n其實唔洗好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋好多人都係自學。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有經驗的老屎忽</span></span><br />\n因為小弟不才，無搞過放映會嘅經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=7faca31e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n其實青衣有好大個連儂牆👾 （其實係橋先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），仲有好多空間做到更加多嘅嘢，希望大家可以一齊發表下唔同睇法👀🧠 <br />\n<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;💻歡迎加入👩🏼&zwj;💻<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=7faca31e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NU6xMhU8jR3OnGVlppiJBA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Umuektn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmuektn.jpg&h=638ab841&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a506b1b9396333bdfb345e05e12499f1004a27e9","tid":1471071,"uid":171992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72f65b30e34026ac7af18dd20507eee5e5830